title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - H-60 project - version 1.2
description:
In this addon spotlight we are going to look at the H-60 project which has been released yesterday. The project contains two types of helicopters the MH-60 Romeo and the UH-60 Blackhawk. Both helicopters are provided with multiple liveries.

After having a look at the interior and exterior we are trying to take off with the helicopter which is kind of a challenge but eventually we are going airborne after a few attempts.

If you want to also add these to helicopters to MSFS 2020 download it via the link below:
https://flightsim.to/file/21192/native-h-60-project-wip
